<p>Well hello, weary traveler!</p>
<p>So I decided to finally get off my ass and make the Tiddlywiki embedded images external and use the `_canonical_uri` field to link them up so they behave like they're natively embeddded. The advantage should reduce the load time of this html document //considerably//. Other work has been started to get more things organized the way they should have been from the beginning.</p>
